name: Anusha weds Srikanth
body:
### Hi there!
If you are seeing this, then you have caught us in the middle of development! 
We'd love to give you some goodies at the wedding for being such a curious-cat ;) 

Check back in a day and you won't be disappointed.

P.S. See you at our wedding!
